target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002710_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Quel plaisir de vous revoir<var 1D /var>! On m'a demandé de réquisitionner des unités d'assistance de toute urgence, alors j'ai fait aussi vite que j'ai pu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002720_URIANGER<tab>A welcome contribution. Thine initiative never ceaseth to amaze.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002720_URIANGER<tab>Merci pour votre travail remarquable. C'est très agréable de pouvoir compter sur vous en toutes cir<var 16 /var>cons<var 16 /var>tan<var 16 /var>ces.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002730_LIVINGWAY<tab>Oh, stop! You're making me blush!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002730_LIVINGWAY<tab>Héhé... Mais non, voyons... C'est tout naturel<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002740_LIVINGWAY<tab>Even now as we pursue new dreams, aiding the people of Etheirys remains our greatest joy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002740_LIVINGWAY<tab>Depuis peu, nous sommes à la recherche de nouveaux rêves à réaliser. Mais il n'y a pas à dire, aider les humains, c'est bien ce qui nous procure le plus grand plaisir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002750_LIVINGWAY<tab>Though we have fulfilled the purpose given to us by Hydaelyn, aiding the people of Etheirys remains our greatest joy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002750_LIVINGWAY<tab>Même si la mission que nous avait confiée Hydaelyn est accomplie, c'est toujours un grand plaisir d'aider les humains<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002760_LIVINGWAY<tab>So you can count on us, ever and always!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002760_LIVINGWAY<tab>Vous pouvez nous demander absolument tout ce que vous voulez<var 1D /var>! On ne vous décevra jamais, foi de Livingway<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002770_LIVINGWAY<tab>Right, so! We originally deployed these supporters to patrol the moon and keep it safe.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002770_LIVINGWAY<tab>Comme vous le savez, la fonction première de ces unités d'assistance est d'assurer la sécurité sur la lune.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002780_LIVINGWAY<tab>They've never tussled with voidsent before, but with sufficient data, they ought to hold their own against the ghastly fiends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002780_LIVINGWAY<tab>Elles n'ont jamais combattu de créatures du néant, mais je peux vous assurer qu'avec quelques ajustements, elles seront largement à la hauteur<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002790_LIVINGWAY<tab>Practical, tactical data, acquired in the moment. And who better to give the supporters an educational thrashing than the champion of Etheirys?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002790_LIVINGWAY<tab>Dites-moi, qui parmi vous connaît le mieux ce genre de monstres<var 1D /var>? J'aurais besoin d'une petite dé<var 16 /var>mon<var 16 /var>stra<var 16 /var>tion pour déterminer les points à améliorer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002800_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>I believe I would make a better instructor.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002800_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>L'honneur me revient d'office.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002810_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Not only have I fought voidsent─I am one.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002810_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Si je connais bien les créatures du néant<var 1D /var>? Leur sang coule dans mes veines<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002820_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Well don't just stand there, engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002820_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Euh, j'ai pas tout compris mais... À l'attaque<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002830_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Engage, engage, engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002830_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Pas de quartier<var 1D /var>! Sus à l'ennemi<var 1D /var>! Yahaa<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002840_LIVINGWAY<tab>That'll do! That'll do!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002840_LIVINGWAY<tab>Pouce<var 1D /var>! Pouce<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002850_LIVINGWAY<tab>A defeat bitterer than the bitterest carrot... Using this experience, we must enhance the supporters and turn them into voidsent slaughter-bots!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002850_LIVINGWAY<tab>Nom d'une carotte, quelle cuisante défaite... Si on veut éviter la raclée contre les créatures du néant, ces machines vont avoir besoin d'un sérieux coup de neuf<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002860_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Indeed... Right after we've managed to put the poor dears back together.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002860_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Euh... Avant de penser à les améliorer, on va d'abord devoir les réparer. Et il y a du boulot...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002870_URIANGER<tab>Pray forgive our comrade's enthusiasm. May I inquire as to how long the repairs will take?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002870_URIANGER<tab>Toutes nos excuses, Zero y est allée un peu fort... À combien estimez-vous le délai nécessaire pour les remettre en état de fonc<var 16 /var>tion<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002880_MAPPINGWAY<tab>On an ordinary day, I'd say no less than five carrots, briskly consumed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002880_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Ça dépend. À vue de nez, je dirais environ... cinq carottes, s'il n'y a pas d'imprévu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002890_MAPPINGWAY<tab>But if you were to provide us with encouragement...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002890_MAPPINGWAY<tab>À moins que... Avec vos encouragements pour nous stimuler...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002900_MAPPINGWAY<tab>We just might be able to do it in two.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002900_MAPPINGWAY<tab>On pourrait peut-être terminer en deux carottes tout pile<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002910_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>This, I leave to you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002910_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>À toi de jouer, cette fois.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002920_YSHTOLA<tab>Can you hear me? We've just finished restoring the brands.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002920_YSHTOLA<tab>(-Y'shtola-)Allô, tu m'entends<var 1D /var>? La réparation des glaives est terminée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002930_YSHTOLA<tab>Let us reconvene once you've finished tending to matters there. The culmination of our efforts is nigh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002930_YSHTOLA<tab>(-Y'shtola-)Venez me retrouver quand vous en aurez fini de votre côté. C'est l'heure d'ouvrir notre passage vers le néant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002950_YSHTOLA<tab>(-Y'shtola-)Apologies for the wait. The preparations here are finally complete.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002950_YSHTOLA<tab>(-Y'shtola-)Vous me recevez<var 1D /var>? Tout est en place de notre côté.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002960_ALPHINAUD<tab>Excellent. The tower too is activated. But give the word, and we will begin channeling the aether.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002960_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nous sommes prêts, nous aussi. La tour est activée et nous n'attendons que ton signal pour envoyer l'éther.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002970_YSHTOLA<tab>(-Y'shtola-)Very well, then. Make it so.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002970_YSHTOLA<tab>(-Y'shtola-)Très bien, allez-y.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002980_ALISAIE<tab>The moment of truth!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002980_ALISAIE<tab>C'est parti mon kiki<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002990_NIDHANA<tab>By the Sisters...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002990_NIDHANA<tab>Tout cet éther, c'est incroyable<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003000_YSHTOLA<tab>Urianger, commence your invocations. 'Tis time to open our gate!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003000_YSHTOLA<tab>Urianger, tu es prêt<var 1D /var>? C'est le moment de lancer l'incantation<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003010_YSHTOLA<tab>A tear is beginning to form! Quickly, activate the brands!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003010_YSHTOLA<tab>La fissure dimensionnelle est en train de se former<var 1D /var>! À toi d'activer les glaives<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003020_YSHTOLA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003020_YSHTOLA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003030_YSHTOLA<tab>Success... The gate is open, and the seal appears to be in place...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003030_YSHTOLA<tab>Ça y est, la porte est ouverte... La barrière semble fonctionner normalement...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003040_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Let's see how well it holds.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003040_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Reste à voir si elle aura l'efficacité espérée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003050_VOIDSENT04735<tab>What an enormous gate! Lord Golbez will be eager to hear of this!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003050_VOIDSENT04735<tab>Le seigneur Golbez avait raison... Cette porte est immense<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003060_VOIDSENT04735<tab>So this is the promised land... The land of boundless aether!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003060_VOIDSENT04735<tab>La voilà, notre terre promise... Et un festin d'éther à volonté<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003070_VOIDSENT04735<tab>Arrrgh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003070_VOIDSENT04735<tab>Yaaargh<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003080_URIANGER<tab>I daresay the seal doth serve its purpose.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003080_URIANGER<tab>Il n'aura pas fallu attendre longtemps pour obtenir la preuve que la barrière fonctionne comme prévu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003090_VRITRA<tab>I see all proceedeth apace. Remarkable...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003090_VRITRA<tab>Mes excuses pour le retard. Je vois que tout semble aller pour le mieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003100_YSHTOLA<tab>Indeed. Just this moment, a voidsent emerged from the gate─by which we may safely assume it leads to the Thirteenth.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003100_YSHTOLA<tab>Oui, l'entité qui vient de franchir notre porte prouve qu'elle débouche bien sur le treizième reflet.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003110_NIDHANA<tab>It's incredible, Y'shtola! Truly incredible! Oh, what an honor it is to have been part of this historic achievement!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003110_NIDHANA<tab>Formidable, Y'shtola<var 1D /var>! Nous sommes honorés de pouvoir être témoins d'un tel moment<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003120_YSHTOLA<tab>A part is an understatement. None of this would have been possible without you and yours.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003120_YSHTOLA<tab>Merci à vous tous. Rien n'aurait été possible sans votre aide précieuse.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003130_YSHTOLA<tab>Our success has also served to solidify our understanding of cross-rift travel.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003130_YSHTOLA<tab>Ce succès nous permet également d'asseoir les bases théoriques du principe de saut dimensionnel.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003140_YSHTOLA<tab>The Ascians rejoined reflections to the Source by instigating elemental imbalances. These imbalances weakened the barrier between realities, causing the aether of a reflection to flood the Source.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003140_YSHTOLA<tab>Comme nous le savons, la stratégie de réunification des Asciens consistait à rompre l'équilibre élémentaire des reflets afin que leur éther rejoigne le monde primitif.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003150_YSHTOLA<tab>But why is it that reflections are predisposed to rejoin the Source? Why have they never merged with one another?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003150_YSHTOLA<tab>Mais vous êtes-vous déjà demandé pourquoi cette énergie se déverse immanquablement vers notre monde, et non ses reflets<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003160_URIANGER<tab>Thou art suggesting there is a unique property inherent to the Source─one responsible for such an outcome?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003160_URIANGER<tab>... Peut-être parce que notre planète est animée par une force très par<var 16 /var>ti<var 16 /var>cu<var 16 /var>liè<var 16 /var>re, qu'on ne retrouve nulle part ailleurs<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003170_YSHTOLA<tab>I am. 'Tis my conclusion that, as the point of origin for the reflections, the Source has an innate “pull” over them.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003170_YSHTOLA<tab>Oui, je suis partie du même postulat. Puisque le monde originel formait un tout, il est possible qu'Ætherys exerce une sorte de magnétisme sur les reflets pour retrouver sa forme première.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003180_YSHTOLA<tab>Hydaelyn, I believe, sought to suppress that pull, which is why She was created with the power of Light─of stasis.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003180_YSHTOLA<tab>Ce serait pour réfréner cette attraction et empêcher la réunification des mondes qu'Hydaelyn a été créée sous le signe de la Lumière, l'élément re<var 16 /var>pré<var 16 /var>sen<var 16 /var>tant la stagnation.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003190_YSHTOLA<tab>Meanwhile, the power of Darkness─of activity─reigns in the void. Hydaelyn's influence would naturally be weaker, and this manifested in the form of planar fissures.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003190_YSHTOLA<tab>Dans le même temps, le néant penche clairement du côté des Ténèbres, qui symbolisent l'évolution. Cela ex<var 16 /var>pli<var 16 /var>que<var 16 /var>rait la faible emprise d'Hydaelyn sur le treizième reflet, et la formation naturelle de fissures vers celui-ci.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003200_YSHTOLA<tab>Working with this hypothesis, I set my sights upon where the pull was assessed to be strongest. And through our combined efforts, we succeeded in opening a gate to the void.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003200_YSHTOLA<tab>C'est en me basant sur ces hypothèses que j'ai déterminé où se trouvait l'attraction la plus forte, afin d'ouvrir notre porte vers le néant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003210_YSHTOLA<tab>Now, I must stress: it was because we sought the void that we succeeded. Pleased though I am to have my theory proven, the secrets of travel to other reflections still elude us.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003210_YSHTOLA<tab>Certes, mon plan a fonctionné et nous a procuré de nouvelles certitudes, mais je doute fortement qu'il puisse nous servir à voyager vers un autre reflet que le treizième.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003220_YSHTOLA<tab>Even so, in the reality that lies beyond the Eighth Umbral Calamity, there are those who found a way to reach the First. I will not rest until I do the same.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003220_YSHTOLA<tab>Et pourtant, dans le futur du huitième fléau, certains ont réussi à transcender les dimensions pour rallier le premier reflet... Je dois continuer mes recherches pour percer leur secret<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003230_ESTINIEN<tab>One step closer to fulfilling your dream, eh?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003230_ESTINIEN<tab>Notre chère Y'shtola s'approche encore un peu plus de son grand rêve de voyager entre les mondes, hm<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003240_YSHTOLA<tab>Just a step. Many more remain to be taken.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003240_YSHTOLA<tab>Si seulement<var 1D /var>! Il reste encore tant de chemin à parcourir...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003250_YSHTOLA<tab>Which further motivates me to forestall a voidsent invasion. So come, let us set forth─to find Azdaja, and put an end to Golbez's plot!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003250_YSHTOLA<tab>Et je n'ai aucunement l'intention de laisser les habitants du néant me gêner<var 1D /var>! Partons vite sauver Azdaja et mettre fin aux ambitions de Golbez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003260_VRITRA<tab>Climb upon my back. I shall take us to the gate.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003260_VRITRA<tab>Je vous en prie, montez sur mon dos. Nous allons descendre ensemble au fond du cratère.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003270_URIANGER<tab>As we did discuss prior, I shall see the alchemists safely home, then together with the Loporrits, maintain vigil over the gate.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003270_URIANGER<tab>Pour ma part, je vais rac<var 16 /var>com<var 16 /var>pag<var 16 /var>ner nos amis alchimistes avant d'organiser la sur<var 16 /var>veil<var 16 /var>lan<var 16 /var>ce de la porte avec les Loporrites.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003280_NIDHANA<tab>May the Sisters watch over and keep you safe!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003280_NIDHANA<tab>Surtout, soyez prudents<var 1D /var>! Nous prierons pour que vous nous reveniez tous sains et saufs<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003290_VRITRA<tab>Unto the void once more!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003290_VRITRA<tab>En route pour le treizième reflet<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003300_YSHTOLA<tab>This is the moon of the Thirteenth?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003300_YSHTOLA<tab>Nous y voilà... La lune du treizième reflet...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003310_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>It is. Ever since the Flood, it has been a sanguinary orb in the sky.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003310_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Oui, aucun doute. Je reconnaîtrais entre mille cette couleur sanglante que lui a donnée le déluge de Ténèbres...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003320_ESTINIEN<tab>No voidsent. A rather more subdued reception than I had anticipated.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003320_ESTINIEN<tab>Dites, c'est le calme plat, par ici. Moi qui m'attendais à être accueilli par une horde d'entités...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003330_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>But unsurprising, given how jealously Golbez conceals the location of his domain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003330_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Seuls les plus fidèles lieutenants de Golbez savent où se trouve son repaire. Rien de surprenant à ce que l'endroit soit désert.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003340_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Still, we must remain on guard. One of his minions came through the gate, after all, and more may lie in wait.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003340_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Mais ne relâchons pas notre attention pour autant... Comme cette créature qui est passée plus tôt, d'autres ennemis nous attendent peut-être, tapis dans l'ombre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003350_VRITRA<tab>I do not sense my sister... Where could she be? Where?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003350_VRITRA<tab>Où est ma sœur<var 1D /var>!? Je ne la vois pas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003360_ESTINIEN<tab>Steady, Vrtra. We've barely arrived. Let us explore our surrounds before drawing conclusions.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003360_ESTINIEN<tab>Tu dois garder ton sang-froid, Vrtra. Commençons par inspecter les environs, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003370_VRITRA<tab>Yes... Thou art right.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003370_VRITRA<tab>Tu as raison, je me suis emporté...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003380_VRITRA<tab>I shall survey the moon from above. The ground, I leave to you all.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003380_VRITRA<tab>Je vais scruter les environs depuis les airs, à vous la battue sur la terre ferme.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003390_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>The chasm has caught your attention as well.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003390_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Toi aussi, tu es <var 08 E905 ((intriguée)) ((intrigué)) /var> par ce cratère<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003400_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>There's some manner of structure below. Worth a look, wouldn't you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003400_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>J'aperçois un édifice, au fond... Tu crois qu'on devrait aller jeter un œil<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003410_YSHTOLA<tab>I too sense something here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003410_YSHTOLA<tab>Cet endroit est plus que suspect...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003420_YSHTOLA<tab>This pit much resembles the Cradle of Darkness on our moon, where Zodiark was once imprisoned.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003420_YSHTOLA<tab>Ce cratère ressemble étrangement au Berceau des Ténèbres de Mare Lamentorum, là où était emprisonné Zordiarche...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003430_YSHTOLA<tab>If this place serves the same function, then a fragment of His power must have been sealed in the depths.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003430_YSHTOLA<tab>Il est donc probable qu'il renfermait jusqu'à récemment une fraction de l'énergie du Primordial.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003440_YSHTOLA<tab>Strange, though. When Zodiark perished in the Source, I presumed that every aspect of Him was thus unmade, and His power scattered.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003440_YSHTOLA<tab>Depuis son ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment dans le monde primitif, je pensais qu'il ne restait plus trace de sa présence dans les reflets.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003450_YSHTOLA<tab>But it's unmistakable, the Darkness that permeates this abyss. Could a trace of Him yet remain...or is it something else?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003450_YSHTOLA<tab>Pourtant, une intense énergie de Ténèbres émane du fond de ce cratère. Serait-ce un résidu de Zordiarche<var 1D /var>? Ou alors...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003460_VRITRA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003460_VRITRA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003470_VRITRA<tab>I hear thee, Sister! I hear thee!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003470_VRITRA<tab>Azdaja<var 1D /var>! C'est toi<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003480_VRITRA<tab>Climb on, my friends! Azdaja is here, within this chasm!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003480_VRITRA<tab>Vite, montez sur mon dos<var 1D /var>! Ma sœur est au fond de ce cratère<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003490_VRITRA<tab>Sister!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003490_VRITRA<tab>Azdaja<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003500_VRITRA<tab>'Tis I, Vrtra! I have come to rescue thee!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003500_VRITRA<tab>Tu m'entends<var 1D /var>!? Je suis venu te sauver<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003510_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>You were entrusted with Azdaja's eye, were you not?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003510_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Tu as toujours l'œil avec toi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003520_AZDAJA<tab>What? How...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003520_AZDAJA<tab>Où suis-je...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003530_AZDAJA<tab>Vrtra...? Wherefore art thou here...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003530_AZDAJA<tab>Vrtra...<var 1D /var>? C'est vraiment toi...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003540_VRITRA<tab>Oh, thank goodness!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003540_VRITRA<tab>Oh, Azdaja<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003550_VRITRA<tab>'Tis thee, dear sister. Truly thee... How long have I dreamed of this moment!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003550_VRITRA<tab>Ma chère soeur<var 1D /var>! Tu m'as tellement manqué<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003560_VRITRA<tab>Would that I could have found thee sooner...but I am here now. Let us return home, together.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003560_VRITRA<tab>Mes amis et moi sommes venus te chercher. Viens, rentrons ensemble dans notre monde...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003570_AZDAJA<tab>The thought filleth me with joy...but I fear it cannot be. Not even with a dragon's might can these chains be broken.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003570_AZDAJA<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, c'est impossible... Même la force des dragons anciens ne peut briser cet envoûtement...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003580_AZDAJA<tab>For they are forged of the very will of the man named Golbez.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003580_AZDAJA<tab>Mes liens sont aussi inflexibles que la volonté de cet homme qui se fait appeler Golbez...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003590_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>So this is indeed Golbez's domain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003590_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Nous nous trouvons donc bien sur le territoire de Golbez.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003600_AZDAJA<tab>Thou keepest company with mortals?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003600_AZDAJA<tab>Mon frère... Te serais-tu allié aux humains...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003610_VRITRA<tab>I do. They are my stalwart allies, without whom I could not have come this far.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003610_VRITRA<tab>Oui. Ceux-ci sont de précieux compagnons qui m'ont aidé à venir à ta rencontre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003620_AZDAJA<tab>Is that so... Then much time hath passed indeed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003620_AZDAJA<tab>Vraiment<var 1D /var>? Tant d'années ont dû passer...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003630_AZDAJA<tab>It doth feel like only yesterday that we were fighting the voidsent hordes the men of Allag had unleashed on Meracydia...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003630_AZDAJA<tab>À l'époque, une guerre sans merci nous opposait aux Allagois... Les créatures du néant qu'ils avaient invoquées venaient de ravager notre terre, Méracydia.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003640_AZDAJA<tab>Desperate to save Tiamat, I flew into this lightless world to strike at the heart of the Cloud of Darkness's forces.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003640_AZDAJA<tab>Je suis alors venue dans ce monde avec l'espoir de sauver Tiamat, et la ferme intention d'éliminer autant de suppôts du Nuage de Ténèbres que mes forces le permettraient...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003650_AZDAJA<tab>But the voidsent I slew returned again and again. And before I knew it, the rift betwixt worlds had closed. I was stranded. Bereft of strength...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003650_AZDAJA<tab>Hélas, chaque entité que j'abattais revenait à la vie pour m'attaquer de nouveau. Alors que mon combat s'éternisait, la porte entre les mondes se referma. J'étais si faible, et surtout... prisonnière.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003660_VRITRA<tab>Thou didst save the lives of full many, Sister.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003660_VRITRA<tab>La bravoure dont tu as fait preuve devant les forces du néant a permis de sauver nombre de nos congénères, tu sais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003670_VRITRA<tab>Today, we abide in harmony with men, working side by side and forging enduring bonds.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003670_VRITRA<tab>Si les dragons vivent désormais en paix et en<var 16 /var>tre<var 16 /var>tien<var 16 /var>nent des relations amicales avec les humains, c'est aussi grâce à toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003680_VRITRA<tab>Indeed, in the course of searching for thee, I did cross paths with many a noble mortal, with whom I built a nation of rich diversity.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003680_VRITRA<tab>Et je suis bien placé pour le savoir<var 1D /var>! Au fil des rencontres dans ma quête pour retrouver ta trace, j'ai même contribué à la création d'une ville aujourd'hui florissante.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003690_VRITRA<tab>To thee I would show it─my beautiful Radz-at-Han. I shall not rest until thou art free.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003690_VRITRA<tab>Ah, que j'aimerais te montrer ma belle et chère Radz-at-Han... Mais pour cela, il nous faut d'abord briser les liens qui te retiennent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003700_AZDAJA<tab>When Golbez found me collapsed, the Darkness ravaging my wounds, he spoke and said:
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003700_AZDAJA<tab>Golbez est venu à ma rencontre alors que j'agonisais au sol, le pouvoir des Ténèbres rongeant peu à peu mes blessures.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003710_AZDAJA<tab>“'Tis but a matter of time before you turn. But I have the power to stop it.”
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003710_AZDAJA<tab>Après m'avoir annoncé qu'il ne me restait que peu de temps avant de devenir une créature du néant, il m'a proposé d'arrêter la métamorphose... Et j'ai accepté.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003720_AZDAJA<tab>And he did─for a price. I would remain myself, but bound. An everlasting feast for his minions, who supped upon my aether over thousands of years.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003720_AZDAJA<tab>Voilà l'origine du sortilège qui entrave mes mouvements. Si j'ai pu échapper au misérable destin qui m'attendait, cela fait maintenant plusieurs millénaires que je suis la captive de Golbez et qu'il se repaît de mon éther.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003730_ESTINIEN<tab>What now, then? Does this great wyrm intend to remain a captive meal for all eternity, not daring to test her chains?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003730_ESTINIEN<tab>Oh... Et donc, madame la dragonne ancienne compte rester ici pour servir de buffet à volonté jusqu'à la fin de ses jours<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003740_AZDAJA<tab>If such is thine attempt at encouragement, mortal, then thou art as graceless as Nidhogg.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003740_AZDAJA<tab>Quel toupet... Si c'est ta façon de m'encourager, humain, elle me rappelle affreusement celle de mon frère Nidhogg...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003750_AZDAJA<tab>'Twas Golbez who did weave this spell, and so his defeat should serve to unravel it. Would it suffice as a show of spirit were I to reveal what I know of the villain?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003750_AZDAJA<tab>Le seul moyen de rompre cet envoûtement serait de vaincre celui qui l'a fait naître... Si je vous en apprenais davantage au sujet de Golbez, m'aideriez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003760_ESTINIEN<tab>Now there's a start. So, what can you tell us?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003760_ESTINIEN<tab>Peut-être bien. Tu connais son point faible<var 1D /var>? L'endroit où il se planque<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003770_AZDAJA<tab>Mayhap in order to sustain the magick, he cannot travel far from this place.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003770_AZDAJA<tab>J'ignore si c'est pour maintenir son emprise sur moi, mais il ne s'éloigne jamais bien longtemps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003780_AZDAJA<tab>He doth prefer to send minions to carry out his will, but on occasion will himself ascend to the moon's surface.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003780_AZDAJA<tab>Il règle la plupart de ses affaires à distance en donnant des ordres à ses sous-fifres, mais il lui arrive parfois de remonter à la surface...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003790_AZDAJA<tab>And every time, without fail, he will visit the same location to the south. Something of import lieth there, doubt not.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003790_AZDAJA<tab>Lorsque c'est le cas, je ressens invariablement sa présence faire halte au même endroit, au sud d'ici. Ce n'est sûrement pas anodin...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003800_ESTINIEN<tab>Well, you heard her. Shall we look into this spot near and dear to our enemy's heart?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003800_ESTINIEN<tab>Vous avez entendu<var 1D /var>? Je crois qu'on devrait aller inspecter l'endroit en question, histoire de savoir ce qu'il a de si intéressant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003810_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Did you find something?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003810_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Tu as trouvé quelque chose<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003820_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>A memoria. But whose...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003820_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Un mémoria... Mais de qui<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003830_DURANTE<tab>You have lied, pillaged, and murdered. Have you anything to say in your defense?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003830_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)Traîtres, voleurs et assassins, tous autant que vous êtes... Un dernier mot pour ta défense<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003840_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003840_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003850_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>No. Every one of them got what they deserved. Trusting fools.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003850_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>Que veux-tu que je te dise<var 1D /var>? Ceux-là n'ont eu que ce qu'ils méritaient, hé hé... à compter sur les autres...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003860_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>Like you would-be heroes. Aye, you'd do well to keep a close eye on each other.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003860_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>Faites gaffe aussi, vous deux... Les histoires de duo soudé, hé hé... ça ne dure jamais bien longtemps...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003870_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>It always ends the same way. A knife in the back. And better to have the handle towards your hand.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003870_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>Quand on se retrouve avec un couteau planté dans le dos, on se dit qu'on aurait dû frapper le premier... Mais c'est trop tard...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003880_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>You'll see... Oh yes, you will...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003880_MEMORIAMASTERA04661<tab>Vous n'y couperez pas, hé hé...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003890_BARONKNIGHT<tab>...In death, may your soul find salvation.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003890_BARONKNIGHT<tab>... Puisse son âme trouver la voie du salut.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003900_DURANTE<tab>I can't bring myself to pray for the unrepentant. You're a nobler man than I.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003900_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)J'ai pas la moindre envie de prier pour ces types-là... Le seul héros parmi nous, c'est toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003910_BARONKNIGHT<tab>Come now. We are all shaped by these dark times more than we would care to admit.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003910_BARONKNIGHT<tab>Ne dis pas de bêtises, enfin. Tu sais bien que c'est l'époque qui veut ça.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003920_BARONKNIGHT<tab>I choose to believe that, had these men known peace and plenty, they would not have been consumed by mistrust and avarice.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003920_BARONKNIGHT<tab>Si ces hommes n'avaient pas grandi dans le conflit, 
leur cœur ne serait pas gangrené par cette défiance malsaine.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003930_DURANTE<tab>Victims of the Contramemoria then, like so many others. But we will end it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003930_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)Foutue guerre des mémorias... J'espère vraiment qu'on trouvera un moyen d'en finir le plus vite possible.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003940_VOIDPERSON04735<tab>Thank you. I shudder to imagine what might have happened if you hadn't dealt with the dark ones.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003940_VOIDPERSON04735<tab>Merci... Je préfère ne pas imaginer ce qui nous serait arrivé si vous ne les aviez pas arrêtés...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003950_BARONKNIGHT<tab>...Who is that?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003950_BARONKNIGHT<tab>... Qui est-ce<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003960_VOIDPERSON04735<tab>Oh, her. She's like you, I hear. Hunts memoriates taken by Darkness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003960_VOIDPERSON04735<tab>Cette fille<var 1D /var>? Je crois qu'elle combat les manieurs de mémorias malfaisants, comme vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003970_DURANTE<tab>Well, well, a kindred spirit. Perhaps we will finally have a new comrade.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003970_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)Intéressant, non<var 1D /var>? C'est peut-être l'occasion d'agrandir notre équipe.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003980_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>No. I've no interest in working with others, much less someone who looks as suspicious as you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003980_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Non merci. Je ne suis pas naïve au point de suivre des inconnus... surtout quand l'un d'eux dissimule son visage sous un casque noir douteux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003990_BARONKNIGHT<tab>Is that so...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_003990_BARONKNIGHT<tab>Ah bon...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004000_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>...If there's nothing else, I'll be on my way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004000_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Sur ce, je vais reprendre ma route. Adieu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004010_DURANTE<tab>Even when we share the same goal, we can't overcome the mistrust. Such is the way of things─the “wisdom” of our era...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004010_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)Il faut croire que partager le même combat ne suffit pas. Peut-être que, comme tu dis, c'est l'époque qui veut ça...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004020_BARONKNIGHT<tab>Only a precious few memoriates remain who cling to the Light. Would that we could have won her over...
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004020_BARONKNIGHT<tab>C'est rare de rencontrer quelqu'un qui se sert des mémorias pour la paix. 
Dommage, on aurait fait une bonne équipe.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004030_DURANTE<tab>We'll make do, old friend. We have accomplished much already, and another person may well have been more of a hindrance than help.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004030_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)Ne t'en fais pas. Tant qu'on est ensemble toi et moi, tout ira bien. D'ailleurs, rien ne dit qu'on aurait été plus efficaces en trio<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004040_DURANTE<tab>Now then, our work here is finished.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004040_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)Bon... On en a fini avec notre mission dans cette région<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004050_DURANTE<tab>His Majesty has summoned us, so let us not delay. To Baron!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004050_DURANTE<tab>(-Compagnon d'armes-)Puisque le roi nous a ordonné de rentrer au pays dès que possible, je pense que c'est le moment de plier bagage. En route pour Baron<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004060_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Had another vision of the past, did you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004060_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Tu as encore eu une vision du passé<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004070_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>...What? I was in it!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004070_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>... Vraiment, j'étais là<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004080_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>It's them─the pair I met in that village. Which means the one sealed in this memoria is...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004080_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>J'en déduis qu'il s'agit des deux soldats que j'ai rencontrés, dans ce village. Mais alors, ce mémoria...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004090_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>So, you have come. You who would oppose our crusade...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004090_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>C'est donc vous qui osez vous opposer à ma guerre sacrée, depuis votre monde...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004100_VRITRA<tab>Sister!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004100_VRITRA<tab>Azdaja<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004110_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>You... I know you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004110_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Toi... Je te reconnais<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004120_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Is that so? From the world before, I daresay.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004120_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Hm... On se serait rencontrés autrefois<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004130_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>'Tis impressive enough that you have managed to retain your mortal form, but to remember your past besides...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004130_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>C'est déjà rare qu'un humain ayant une part de Ténèbres garde son apparence, mais de là à se souvenir de son passé... Remarquable.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004140_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>But that is of no moment. You are the memoriate who vanquished my minions, correct?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004140_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Dis-moi, tu es bien la manieuse de mémorias qui a vaincu mes généraux, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004150_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>And what if I am?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004150_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Peut-être, et alors<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004160_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Then I would bid you join me. As a child of our world and slave to the wheel, fight with me for the salvation of all our souls.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004160_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Tu es de ce monde, toi aussi. Rejoins-moi dans ma guerre sacrée... Pour le salut de ton âme...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004170_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Fight with you? More like fight as your pawn.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004170_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Hmpf... Que je me range à tes côtés<var 1D /var>? Dis plutôt que tu commences à manquer de pions pour tes manigances.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004180_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>It isn't me you want, but my power. And if I don't obey, you'll bind me like you bound that dragon.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004180_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Ce n'est pas moi que tu veux, c'est mon pouvoir. Et si j'acceptais, je finirais tôt ou tard comme cette dragonne dont tu as fait ton esclave.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004190_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>But no more. I refuse to be bound ever again. I fight only for myself, and for those in whom I trust. My friends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004190_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Assez de ces relations de pur intérêt<var 1D /var>! Mon seul combat, je le mène pour ceux à qui la confiance m'unit<var 1D /var>: mes amis<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004200_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>I see. A pity.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004200_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Je vois... Dommage pour toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004210_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>It is for the dragon that you have come, yes?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004210_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Vous êtes venus pour cette dragonne, je présume<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004220_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>When first you appeared, I thought simply to remove a threat to our plan.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004220_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Quand j'ai entendu parler de vous, j'ai d'abord ordonné à mes généraux de vous éliminer pour éviter que vous n'entraviez mes plans. Mais puisque vous m'avez fait l'honneur de venir jusqu'ici...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004230_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Never did I imagine that you would reach this place, and gift me a golden opportunity!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004230_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>L'occasion est trop belle pour ne pas en profiter<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004240_VRITRA<tab>Speak plainly, gaoler.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004240_VRITRA<tab>Comment ça<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004250_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004250_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004260_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Long as it has been imprisoned, this dragon has grown feeble and weak, its spirit extinguished.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004260_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Une éternité s'est écoulée depuis que j'ai fait mienne cette dragonne... Et alors qu'elle arrive au bout de ses forces, voilà que vous faites votre apparition...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004270_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Your coming has served to rekindle her forgotten hope.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004270_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Il va sans dire que votre venue a eu pour effet de faire renaître l'espoir en elle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004280_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Her yearning to be free─to return home! That is the key to our deliverance!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004280_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Elle désire plus que tout rentrer dans son monde parmi les siens... C'est là que se trouve la clef pour accomplir l'ultime salut<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004290_VRITRA<tab>Azdaja! No!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004290_VRITRA<tab>Qu'est-ce qui lui arrive...<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004300_YSHTOLA<tab>The Darkness is ravaging her! She's becoming a voidsent!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004300_YSHTOLA<tab>L'éther de Ténèbres est en train de la ronger... Elle va se transformer en créature du néant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004310_AZDAJA<tab>Vrtra... Thou must flee!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004310_AZDAJA<tab>Vrtra...<var 1D /var>! Va-t'en<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004320_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Rise, O Shadow Dragon, and obey!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004320_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Magnifique<var 1D /var>! Plie-toi à mes ordres, dragonne obscure<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004330_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Kill him.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004330_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Tue-le.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004340_VRITRA<tab>Sister, please!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004340_VRITRA<tab>Azdaja, non<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004350_ESTINIEN<tab>Damn you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004350_ESTINIEN<tab>Ordure<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004360_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Keep our guests occupied.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004360_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Amusez-vous avec ces pitoyables humains.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004370_VRITRA<tab>Save her, I beg thee... Save my sister...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004370_VRITRA<tab>Ma sœur... Aide-la, je t'en supplie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004380_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Before Darkness swallowed the world, I fought tirelessly in a war without end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004380_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Avant que ce monde ne soit englouti par les Ténèbres, j'ai consacré ma vie à combattre dans une guerre sans fin...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004390_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>The experience taught me to discern the strong. That dragon...and you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004390_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>C'est pourquoi à l'instant où j'ai posé les yeux sur toi, j'ai compris. Ici, outre le dragon, c'est toi mon <var 08 E905 ((ennemie la plus dangereuse)) ((ennemi le plus dangereux)) /var>.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004400_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Come. Face me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004400_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Tu es <var 08 E905 ((prête)) ((prêt)) /var>, <var 08 E905 ((humaine)) ((humain)) /var><var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_Q4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_Q4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_A4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Rest assured I need no invitation.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_A4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Nous sommes venus mettre fin à tes plans maléfiques<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_A4_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'll deal with you, and then I'll free Azdaja.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_A4_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je te vaincrai, et Azdaja pourra enfin retrouver sa liberté.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004410_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Accursed Light...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004410_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Quelle lueur répugnante...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004420_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>You who have ever basked in its warmth could never understand our envy! Our agony!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004420_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Toi et les tiens avez toujours vécu dans la Lumière. Vous n'avez pas idée de ce que j'ai traversé... de ce que ce monde a enduré<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004430_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>You will not deny us our release!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004430_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Je ne te laisserai pas faire obstacle à ma destinée. Ma guerre sacrée n'aura qu'une seule issue... l'ultime salut<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004440_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Expect no mercy. To destroy you, I shall bring my all to bear!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004440_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Hmm... Je ne retiendrai pas mes coups pour t'éliminer...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004445_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Come, warriors from beyond the rift!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004445_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>En garde, <var 08 E905 ((combattante)) ((combattant)) /var> d'un autre monde<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004450_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>My power...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004450_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Urgh... Mes forces m'abandonnent...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004455_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Even my blade... So this is the limit of my defiance...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004455_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Et même mon épée... C'est donc ici... que tout s'arrête...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004460_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Are you all right!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004460_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Tout va bien<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004470_ESTINIEN<tab>What's happening!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004470_ESTINIEN<tab>Vous avez entendu ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004480_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Hahaha... Ahahahahaha!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004480_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Mwahahahahahaha<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004490_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>At last, the moment is at hand...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004490_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Nous voilà enfin au moment... de l'apothéose...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004500_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>You may have bested me, but not quickly enough. Too late will you look to the chasm.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004500_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Malgré ma défaite, j'ai réussi à vous tenir éloignés des profondeurs du cratère...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004510_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>You've won the battle, but I win the war!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004510_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>L'issue de ma guerre sacrée ne fait plus aucun doute<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004520_VRITRA<tab>Stop this, I beg of thee! Let her go!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004520_VRITRA<tab>Non... Laisse-la... Par pitié...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004530_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Darkness made manifest once abided in the depths of this abyss. Until, one day, it dispersed in a haze of aether.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004530_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Une gigantesque incarnation des Ténèbres sommeillait au fond de ce cratère... mais elle vient de disparaître.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004540_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>In the absence of the great flow, that aether has nowhere to return.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004540_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Seulement, dans notre monde, l'éther n'a nul endroit où retourner...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004550_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>And so it has coalesced, giving rise to a mighty voidsent!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004550_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Tout être qui s'éteint renaît en créature du néant, sans exception<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004560_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Now, feast! Feast upon this dragon, and its ardent longing for home with it!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004560_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Dévore cette dragonne<var 1D /var>! Et avec elle, son vœu ardent de retrouver sa terre natale<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004570_VRITRA<tab>Nooooooooo!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004570_VRITRA<tab>Noooon<var 1D /var>!!!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004580_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>From the convergence of ancient and newborn, an entity without equal shall emerge─one who shall tear down the barrier between worlds!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004580_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Votre amie exilée ne fera bientôt qu'un avec les Ténèbres... Ensemble, ils donneront naissance à un être transcendant les mondes<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004590_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Upon you, who shall deliver us from eternal damnation, I bestow the name of a hero of eld!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004590_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>À toi qui guidera les âmes du néant au cycle de la vie dont elles ont toujours été exclues... j'offre le nom de notre héros des temps anciens<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004600_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Zeromus! Awaken!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004600_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Viens au monde, Zeromus<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004610_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>No matter how powerful, a voidsent can be sealed in memoria!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004610_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Peu importe sa taille, je dois pouvoir le transformer en mémoria<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004620_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004620_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004630_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Damn it... It's too strong...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004630_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Bon sang<var 1D /var>! Mon pouvoir n'a aucun effet<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004640_YSHTOLA<tab>Our warding scales may not hold! Not against a voidsent born of Zodiark's aether!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004640_YSHTOLA<tab>Ce monstre est né de l'éther de Zordiarche... Nos écailles garde-âme risquent de ne pas faire le poids<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004650_VRITRA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004650_VRITRA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004660_VRITRA<tab>We must retreat! Everyone, to me!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004660_VRITRA<tab>Il vaut mieux battre en retraite<var 1D /var>! Tous, sur mon dos<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004670_VRITRA<tab>I will return, Sister, and I will save thee. This I swear!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004670_VRITRA<tab>On reviendra te sauver, Azdaja... Je te le promets<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004680_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004680_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004690_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004690_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004700_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Do you remember Ciriatto and Farfarello? The cowardly pair of voidsent that dwelled in my domain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004700_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Tu te souviens de Farfarello et Ciriatto<var 1D /var>? Les deux pleutres qui vivaient sur mon territoire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004710_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Ciriatto devoured Farfarello.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004710_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Quand Ciriatto a dévoré l'âme de Farfarello...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004720_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>And in so doing, he inherited an all-consuming fear of Barbariccia.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004720_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Il a aussi hérité de sa peur maladive de Barbariccia.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004730_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>For as you know, when a voidsent is devoured, it doesn't simply cease to be. Its soul persists within the devourer.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004730_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>C'est ce qui arrive quand une créature du néant en absorbe une autre. Les deux âmes se mélangent et n'en forment plus qu'une.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004740_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>And when a voidsent dies, all the souls that harbored may break free to become individual entities once more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004740_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Et lorsque l'entité ainsi créée meurt à son tour, il arrive parfois que les âmes se détachent... et reviennent à la vie séparément.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004750_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>That is to say, by defeating Zeromus, we may yet save Azdaja.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004750_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Là où je veux en venir, c'est qu'en terrassant Zeromus, on aurait un espoir de récupérer l'âme d'Azdaja.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004760_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>And to make certain that we do, we must remind her of who she is.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004760_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Afin de mettre toutes les chances de notre côté, il faudra que ta soeur reprenne conscience d'elle-même.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004770_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>When the time comes, you must call to her. Call with all your being.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004770_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Pour cela, tu devras l'appeler de toutes tes forces. Toi seul peux y parvenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004780_VRITRA<tab>Thy words give me heart, Zero. Thou hast my gratitude.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004780_VRITRA<tab>Merci, Zero. Personne ne connaît mieux le néant que toi, et tes paroles me font chaud au cœur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004790_YSHTOLA<tab>Then it's settled. Our objective is to defeat Zeromus.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004790_YSHTOLA<tab>En ce qui nous concerne, on devra s'atteler à vaincre Zeromus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004800_YSHTOLA<tab>While it is unsettling that a voidsent could be born of Zodiark's aether, its very nature may render it susceptible to the brands that once contained Him. Did Urianger have aught to say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004800_YSHTOLA<tab>Je n'arrive toujours pas à croire qu'un reste de Zordiarche ait engendré une entité nouvelle... Au moins, nous pouvons espérer que les glaives remplissent leur fonction. Tu en as parlé avec Urianger<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004810_YSHTOLA<tab>I see... If the seal may not hold for long, then haste is paramount.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004810_YSHTOLA<tab>Nous n'avons aucune garantie sur le temps qu'ils pourront tenir... Dans ce cas, il va falloir faire au plus vite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004820_ESTINIEN<tab>Couldn't we just let it come to the Source and strike it down here?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004820_ESTINIEN<tab>Et qu'est-ce que vous diriez de lui tomber sur le râble quand il se pointera dans notre monde<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004830_YSHTOLA<tab>Doing so would consign Azdaja's soul to the aetherial sea. Any attempt to ensure her survival demands that we deal with Zeromus in the Thirteenth.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004830_YSHTOLA<tab>Impossible, l'âme d'Azdaja retournerait à la mer des étoiles... Pour la sauver, nous devons absolument terrasser Zeromus dans le treizième reflet.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004840_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>I could barely go near it, never mind land a blow, so thick was the shroud of Darkness. How do you propose we fight such a foe?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004840_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Dans le néant, ce monstre est entouré de Ténèbres qu'il peut manipuler à sa guise. Je n'ai pas pu l'approcher, et encore moins le blesser... Comment comptes-tu le vaincre<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004850_YSHTOLA<tab>Simple. Against impenetrable Darkness, we must wield resplendent Light.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004850_YSHTOLA<tab>La réponse est on ne peut plus évidente. Pour dissiper des Ténèbres abyssales, quoi de mieux qu'une Lumière intense<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004860_YSHTOLA<tab>And it just so happens there is a world replete with Light.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004860_YSHTOLA<tab>Et il se trouve que nous connaissons justement un monde qui en regorge.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004870_YSHTOLA<tab>The question of how we will harness that Light you may leave to me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004870_YSHTOLA<tab>Pour ce qui est de canaliser le pouvoir de la Lumière du premier reflet, faites-moi confiance, je m'occupe de tout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004880_YSHTOLA<tab>With our recent discoveries and proven techniques, as well as the aid of comrades near and far, I have faith that we will find a way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004880_YSHTOLA<tab>Avec mes recherches sur la théorie du saut dimensionnel et l'aide de quelques amis, ça devrait bien se passer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004890_YSHTOLA<tab>But only if I begin my work at once. Rest up while you can, for there will be much to do when I return.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004890_YSHTOLA<tab>Je vais devoir m'absenter quelque temps, mais comptez sur moi, j'aurai de quoi vous occuper en revenant. Reposez-vous bien, car vous en aurez besoin.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004900_ESTINIEN<tab>It wouldn't do to be idle while our esteemed sorceress labors tirelessly. I shall be training if you have need of me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004900_ESTINIEN<tab>Quand notre mère miqo'te prend cet air, c'est du sérieux. Je retourne m'entraîner, et je te conseille d'en faire de même.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004910_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Wait.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004910_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Attends.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004920_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Allow me to join you. I must become stronger for what lies ahead.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004920_MYSTERIOUSPERSON<tab>Laisse-moi t'accompagner. Moi aussi, je veux devenir plus forte.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004930_ESTINIEN<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004930_ESTINIEN<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004940_ESTINIEN<tab>Fine by me. Come on, then.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004940_ESTINIEN<tab>Ça, c'est le genre d'attitude qui me plaît. Allez, viens.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004950_VRITRA<tab>I shall not pass my time wallowing in despair. Using my vessel, I shall attend what preparations I may.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004950_VRITRA<tab>Si tout le monde s'affaire, hors de question que je reste planté ici à attendre. Je vais réinvestir le corps de Varshahn pour préparer ce qui peut l'être.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004960_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Meanwhile, on the moon of the Thirteenth...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004960_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Pendant ce temps, sur la lune du treizième reflet

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004970_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Zeromus is risen, but not yet at full strength. It will take time before the fiend is able to breach the veil.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004970_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Malgré son avènement, Zeromus est encore plongé dans une profonde léthargie... Il lui faudra du repos avant de briser la cloison qui sépare les mondes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004980_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>But what is another moment on this long journey I have endured.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004980_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Un simple contretemps, après tant de chemin parcouru...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004990_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>It remains as fresh as if it were yesterday, old friend. The memory of your passing...and the pain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_004990_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Jamais je n'oublierai ce jour tragique qui t'a vu succomber...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_005000_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>As I promised you then, I promise you now: they shall sing of Golbez─the hero who shattered the wheel and brought salvation to the world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_005000_BLACKKNIGHT<tab>Quoi qu'il arrive, le seul héros qui sauvera ce monde, c'est toi, Golbez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002940_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>（★未使用／削除予定★）
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06400_002940_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>（★未使用／削除予定★）
